| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4791 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5ee3d1e8-80b1-5803-8478-22ba93e88d25"
